    "description": "Hakuyosha Company, Ltd. engages in the cleaning, rental, real estate, and other businesses in Japan. It provides a range of products for home clothing care, including detergents and fabric softeners that are used in home washing machines, as well as insect repellents and clothes covers. The company also rents various linen items, including sheets, towels, tablecloths, and napkins for hotel and restaurant operations, as well as uniforms; and engages in the rental and management of real estate properties. In addition, it offers bedding and interior cleaning services; cleaning and storage services for clothes, such as coats and jackets, as well as for household items comprising carpets and futons; pick-up and delivery cleaning, dry cleaning delivery, and house cleaning services; and used clothing purchase services. Further, the company operates Texcare, which offers maintenance and restoration services; and sells sell machines and materials for cleaning business. The company was founded in 1906 and is headquartered in Ota, Japan."
